About

 
	Blue Bell Private Wealth Management is a fee-only investment management firm located in Blue Bell, Pennsylvania, a nearby suburb of Philadelphia.  As a Registered Investment Advisor (RIA), we have a fiduciary responsibility to act always in the best interest of our clients.With over 80 years combined experience, the partners and team of Blue Bell Private Wealth Management are dedicated to helping our clients maximize their financial goals.  Through a team effort, we seek to build and maintain long-term relationships using constant, effective communication and providing impeccable service.  Our goal is to improve every client�s financial position permanently, simplify their lives and achieve reliable investment results.In order to safeguard client assets, all securities and cash are held off-site by Charles Schwab & Co., Inc.

			


